{"tid":1504014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"In case 唔知邊度走而行左去麗城","createTime":"2019-08-25T07:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:51:01.000Z","uid":74932,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e82346db41bbad1673ac5c6472ba228e34eb5a2","tid":1504014,"uid":74932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"希望有用啦 <br />\n<br />\n麗城巴士有<br />\n34去葵盛東<br />\n234x去尖沙咀，經大部分MTR 紅色線既站<br />\n48x去禾輋，經沙田市中心/城門轉車站有得落<br />\n234b去深井行下路<br />\n53行下路入元朗，經深井黃金海岸屯門<br />\n40x去麗港城，經美孚黃大仙鑽石山九龍灣牛頭角mtr<br />\n<br />\n麗城小巴有<br />\n302去葵芳，經葵興大窩口<br />\n紅van只要頭上寫佐敦道都會去深水埗/mk/油麻地，總站係佐敦寧波街<br />\n96p去荃灣西<br />\n96b去荃灣市中心<br />\n101紅van去荃灣西同楊屋道街市<br />\n<br />\n我唔知巴士路況，有冇停自己check 清楚。有錯請改正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以我所知海濱有238x去尖沙咀，有小巴去青衣。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPlease be safe <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f34461a524e7c6d179244cfd8c2b4178611082","tid":1504014,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0mmSi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0mmSi0.jpg&h=e2509c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJNfyS</a>"},{"pid":"7ee9c2196ff4b6e57eb4b0dfcd56893063f8e29a","tid":1504014,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMMetfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum